 ## Hard Rules
 
 | Prohibited | Required alternative |
 |---|---|
-| Stored procedures / JDBC `callableStatement` | Spring Data JPA + JPQL in `/db/repository/` |
-| Local filesystem writes (`FileWriter`, `/opt/app/...`) | Google Cloud Storage via `Storage` (Spring Cloud GCP) |
-| `while(true)` daemon threads | `@Scheduled` with Virtual Thread executor |
+| Stored procedures / JDBC `callableStatement` | Spring Data JPA + JPQL en `/db/repository/` |
+| Local filesystem writes (`FileWriter`, `/opt/app/...`) | GCS via `IGoogleCloudStorageService` de `jlib-storage` |
+| `while(true)` daemon threads | `@Scheduled` con Virtual Thread executor |
 | `System.out.println` | SLF4J via `@Slf4j` |
 | Hardcoded credentials or business values | Spring Profiles + Secret Manager / constants |
 | Mutable POJOs in domain layer | Java Records (immutable) |
